[1
Date: Wed, 1 Sep 1999 12:45:22 -0500
From: David Henry Zeman <zmans@brookings.net>

[Mod.JW's recommendation of rabies vaccination for petting zoo
and farm animals has one major problem. Rabies vaccines are not
approved for use in those species (by and large) and there is no data on
safety or efficacy.
--
David H. Zeman, DVM, PhD
South Dakota State University
Animal Disease Research and Diagnostic Laboratory
<zmans@brookings.net>
